(79, 78, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032159, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Level 99 announcement', 'When someone hits level 99 in any skill, this will display a message to everyone on the server saying the person who has achieved level 99 and what skill they achieved it in.\n\nHere''s a screenshot:\n[img:2abssrlv]http&#58;//i50&#46;tinypic&#46;com/11wbqxd&#46;png[/img:2abssrlv]\n\n\nNow the code:\n\nOpen your Player class, and find:\n\n[code:2abssrlv]\nint comb = Formulae&#46;getCombatlevel(maxStat);[/code:2abssrlv]Above that, add:\n\n[code:2abssrlv]\n         if(maxStat&#91;i&#93; == 99) {\n            world&#46;sendToAll(getUsername() + &quot; has just achieved level 99 in &quot; + Formulae&#46;statArray&#91;i&#93;);\n         }[/code:2abssrlv]', 'f0e0b59a879162284f5f8fa9014c793b', 0, 'CIA=', '2abssrlv', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(80, 79, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306032184, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'RSCDv25 No Forums mod project', '[img:2718yt0s]http&#58;//img196&#46;imageshack&#46;us/img196/1325/hsp1&#46;png[/img:2718yt0s]\n[img:2718yt0s]http&#58;//img541&#46;imageshack&#46;us/img541/7591/hsp2&#46;png[/img:2718yt0s]\n[img:2718yt0s]http&#58;//img42&#46;imageshack&#46;us/img42/6422/phpcalc&#46;png[/img:2718yt0s]\n\nQ&amp;A\n[quote:2718yt0s]Hi, i tried your rscd www files which you released. However im getting an error : unable to fetch quest information\nIve read your setup tutorial but i just dont get it work.\nThanks[/quote:2718yt0s]You need to create a row in the users table, with the username set as &quot;Guest&quot;. And it says unable to fetch guest info not quest info.\n\n(Updated May 12th/2010)\n--------------------------------------------------------------------\nStand alone RSCDv25 www with no forums --\n\nAll you do is upload the SQL, add a privileged user called &quot;global&quot; pass &quot;12345&quot;, or edit in your own user @ sqlconnect.php\nKeep in mind the default database is also set as &quot;rsca&quot;, (rsc-all).\n\nMain WWW files w/ Forum\nSQL structure (needed)\nNote - Be sure to alter the users table, you need to add a column named &quot;sub_expires&quot; INT(10)\nAlso, make sure you insert a row with the username &quot;Guest&quot;\n\n<!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://darscape.org/forums/downloads.php?do=file&amp;id=45">http://darscape.org/forums/downloads.php?do=file&amp;id=45</a><!-- m -->\n(ALL THREE INCLUDED)\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\nLast Update: May 12, 2010\n* Removed the individual player-view ranking from the pre-packaged website\n* Added web_login table to the SQL structure, forgot to package it originally.\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nSpecial thanks to Luke of RSCEMULATION for aid in SQL and other methods.\n\nWebsite Credits:\n\n* Essential structures, designs, and systems were coded by Sw0o0sh &quot;Tim White&quot;.\n* A special thanks to Kryptix &quot;Luke Leary&quot; for help ensuring website safety, and diagnosing bugs.\n\n[quote:2718yt0s]Website Features:\n\n* Complies to latest web standards, XHTML 1.0 Strict, CSS based web design with SQL/PHP interaction.\n\n* Links perfectly AND ONLY to RSCDv25 Based servers, as well as AND ONLY FLUXBB forums.\n\n* Uses Flux_BB 1.2.22 FORUMS, latest version as of May 08, 2010\nFluxBB Is modified in the following area''s to fit the websites needs:\n-------------------------------------------------------------\n\n(This is listed in case you want to clean install the\nforums yourself,\nor upgrade to a new version... So make sure these changes\nare kept in place.)\n\nstyle/imports/base.css --&gt; 900px wrapper.\ninstall.php --&gt; adds &quot;del_pin&quot; row to DATABASE.potential_prefix.users;\ninstall.php --&gt; PUN_ROOT prefix added before install.php, to fix directory association when installing.\ninclude/functions.php --&gt; (Fixes main navigation links);\nregister.php --&gt; Deleted. Done by website. Added security (captcha), character creation.\nlogin.php --&gt; Deleted. Done by website. Bruteforce security.\n\n--------------------------------------------------------------\n\n* Allows one to host a website without any known worries of SQL injection via forums or website\n(however, always try to stay up-to-date with fluxBB)\n\n* Fully function character management system\n- Fully external character management system (CMS),\ninstead of a hard-to-find character creation page via original RSCD forums.\n- Create, delete, and change passwords of characters flawlessly.\n- The optional feature of a character deletion pin has been added.\n(As the name suggests, the users can not delete their characters without using\nthe deletion pin, IF they decide to set one.)\n- The option of hiding oneself from the highscores.\n\n* Highscores\n- Allows one to search anothers stats, if they are not set to hidden.\n- Allows one to view highscores for all stats and skills.\n- Fixes RSCD based highscores forum where usernames are displayed two or more times, as well.\n\n* Tools\n- A completely PHP based Combat calculator, tested and 100% accurate.\n- Item ID List\n\n* Server Stats\n\n- Displays common stats. Players online, characters, accounts.\n(NOTE: Depending on IF and HOW you fix players online via the GAMESERVER,\nthis display function may not work).\n- Displays totals for RARES. This can be set off.\n\n* Admin Features\n\n- Quickly count multiple server item totals, and see which items belong to who.\n( Links to user securities view bank/inventory feature )\n- Quickly view linked IP address traces/ accounts/characters, for optimum user security.\n( Allows bank / inventory viewing AND wiping via the website )\n- Set stats.\n- Set subscriptions. (An automated system is your job :] )\n- Transfering characters to different accounts.\n( Will make this public eventually )\n\n* Plugin system\n\n- Coming soon, will offer the ability for users to download plugins made by me or anyone else for additional features.\n[/quote:2718yt0s]Code preview : (highscores):\n\n[code:2718yt0s]\n                 case &quot;highscores&quot;&#58;\n                        $grabskill =  isset($_GET&#91;''skill''&#93;) ? trim(strtolower($_GET&#91;''skill''&#93;)) &#58; null;\n                         $search_type = isset($_GET&#91;''type''&#93;) &amp;&amp;  $_GET&#91;''type''&#93; == 1 ? 1 &#58; 0;\n                        $user_search =  empty($_GET&#91;''user''&#93;) ? null &#58; ((strlen($_GET&#91;''user''&#93;) &lt;= 20  &amp;&amp; $search_type == 0 || strlen($_GET&#91;''user''&#93;) &lt;= 11 &amp;  $search_type == 1) ? $_GET&#91;''user''&#93;&#58; null);\n                         echo &quot;&lt;form method=''get'' action=''''&gt;&lt;input type=''hidden''  name=''query'' value=''highscores'' /&gt;&lt;input type=''hidden'' name=''type''  value=''1'' /&gt;&lt;div class=''table''&gt;&lt;div