(119, 118, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033392, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Yong Min''s rebirth base', '[code:hqrqqwia]package org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;npchandler;\n\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;model&#46;*;\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;event&#46;*;\n\npublic class Rebirth implements NpcHandler {\n        /**\n         * Rebirth Base @author Yong Min\n         */\n        public static final World world = World&#46;getWorld();\n        \n        public void handleNpc(final Npc npc, final Player player) throws Exception {\n                if(player&#46;getCombatLevel() &lt;= 99) {\n                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Sorry&#46; You are too low level to use the rebirth system&#46;&quot;, player));\n                    return;\n                }\n                if(player&#46;getReborn() == 1) {\n                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Sorry&#46; You have already been reborn&#46;&quot;, player));\n                    return;\n                }\n                if(player&#46;isAdmin() || player&#46;isMod() || player&#46;isPMod() || player&#46;isEvent()) {\n                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Sorry&#46; Only non-staff accounts can use the rebirth system&#46;&quot;, player));\n                    return;\n                }\n                if(player&#46;getReborn() == 0 &amp;&amp; player&#46;getCombatLevel() &gt;= 100) {\n                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Would you like to be reborn?&quot;, player));\n                    player&#46;setBusy(true);\n                    world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                        public void action() {\n                            player&#46;setBusy(false);\n                            String&#91;&#93; option = new String&#91;&#93; { &quot;What are the requirements to become reborn?&quot;, &quot;What are the benefits of being reborn?&quot;, &quot;Yes, I would like to be reborn&quot;, &quot;No thank you!&quot; };\n                            player&#46;setMenuHandler(new MenuHandler(option) {\n                                public void handleReply(final int option, final String reply) {\n                                    if(player&#46;isBusy()) {\n                                        return;\n                                    }\n                                    player&#46;informOfChatMessage(new ChatMessage(player, reply, npc));\n                                    player&#46;setBusy(true);\n                                    world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                        public void action() {\n                                            player&#46;setBusy(false);\n                                                if(option == 0) {\n                                                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;To become reborn, you need to be level 100+ combat&#46;&quot;, player));\n                                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                            public void action() {\n                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;You will also need to pay 500,000 coins&quot;, player));\n                                                                    world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                        public void action() {\n                                                                            player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;and find 500 rebirth crystals&quot;, player));\n                                                                            npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                                        }\n                                                                    });\n                                                                }\n                                                            });\n                                                        } else if(option == 1) {\n                                                            player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;By becoming reborn, you will gain a faster exp rate,&quot;, player));\n                                                                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                    public void action() {\n                                                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;access to new training areas with better drop rates,&quot;, player));\n                                                                            world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                                public void action() {\n                                                                                    player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;better armour and weapons with increased stats,&quot;, player));\n                                                                                        world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ShortEvent(player) {\n                                                                                            public void action() {\n                                                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;and you will gain access to the Guild of Reborn Warriors&#46;&quot;, player));\n                                                                                                npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                                                            }\n                                                                                        });\n                                                                                    }\n                                                                                });\n                                                                            }\n                                                                        });\n                                                                    } else if(option == 3) {\n                                                                        player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Ok&#46; Come back when you would like to be reborn&#46;&quot;, player));\n                                                                        npc&#46;unblock();\n                                                                    } else if(option == 2 &amp;&amp; player&#46;getInventory()&#46;countId(10) &gt;= 500000 &amp;&amp; player&#46;getInventory()&#46;countId(1329) &gt;= 500) {\n                                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Congratulations&#46; You have now been reborn&#46;&quot;, player));\n                                                                                player&#46;isReborn();\n                                                                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendReborn();\n                                                                                player&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(10, 500000);\n                                                                                player&#46;getInventory()&#46;remove(1329, 500);\n                                                                                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendInventory();\n                                                                            } else if(player&#46;getInventory()&#46;countId(10) &lt; 500000 || player&#46;getInventory()&#46;countId(1329) &lt; 500) {\n                                                                                player&#46;informOfNpcMessage(new ChatMessage(npc, &quot;Sorry, you don''t have all the required items&#46;&quot;, player));\n                                                                        }\n                                                                    }\n                                                                });\n                                                            }\n                                                        });\n                                                        owner&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMenu(option);\n                                                    }\n                                                });\n                                                npc&#46;blockedBy(player);\n                                            }\n                                        }\n                                    }[/code:hqrqqwia][14:19] Yong Min: And also make players names change to [R] Username:\n\n[14:23] Yong Min: And also the damage command will need the godspell objects defining\n\nYou will come across errors pointing to your Player class if you try and compile it, so you will need something like this:\n\n[code:hqrqqwia]\n    /**\n     * Reborn System @author Yong Min\n     */\n    public int reborn = 0;\n\n    public void setReborn(int reborn) {\n        this&#46;reborn = reborn;\n    }\n\n    public int getReborn() {\n        return reborn;\n    }\n\n    public int isReborn() {\n        return reborn = 1;\n    }\n[/code:hqrqqwia][code:hqrqqwia]\nreborn = Integer&#46;parseInt(props&#46;getProperty(&quot;reborn&quot;));\n[/code:hqrqqwia][code:hqrqqwia]\npr&#46;setProperty(&quot;reborn&quot;, &quot;&quot; + this&#46;getReborn());\n[/code:hqrqqwia]As this is set to save the reborn status, you will also need this in your Template.\n\n[code:hqrqqwia]\nreborn=0\n[/code:hqrqqwia]', '9e4d402aa1c7583c9c21ccd1bbb93c4c', 0, 'AIA=', 'hqrqqwia', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(120, 119, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033418, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Trading while updating', 'Ok, some people have noticed that it is very easy to dupe items by trading and logging out while the update timer is running. Here is a basic tutorial how you can prevent people from trading while the timer is running.\n\nThis was an error reported by a friend of mine using an EasyRSC based source, so here is a quick fix.\n\nOpen your World class, and find:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\n    /**\n  * World instance\n  */\n    private static World worldInstance;\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Under that, add:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\n    /**\n  * Update Trading\n  */\n    public static int trading = 0; // 0 can trade, 1 can''t trade - by default, everyone can trade\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Now open your CommandHandler class, and find:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\np&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendAlert(&quot;The server will be shutting down in 60 seconds&#58; &quot; + reason, false);\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Above that, add:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\nWorld&#46;trading = 1; // Set the trading to untradeable\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Now in your TradeHandler class, find:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\n                        case 166&#58; // Sending trade request\n                                affectedPlayer = world&#46;getPlayer(p&#46;readShort());\n                                if(affectedPlayer == null || !player&#46;withinRange(affectedPlayer, 8) || player&#46;isTrading() || player&#46;tradeDuelThrottling()) {\n                                        unsetOptions(player);\n                                        return;\n                                }\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Under that, add:\n\n[code:j63t4rnl]\n       if(World&#46;trading == 1) {\n      player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can''t trade while the server is shutting down for an update&#46;&quot;);\n      return;\n       }\n[/code:j63t4rnl]Here''s a picture of how it is ingame:\n[img:j63t4rnl]http&#58;//i40&#46;tinypic&#46;com/6dy6bb&#46;png[/img:j63t4rnl]', 'c4871496cf519a683393b4a5c6f53758', 0, 'CIA=', 'j63t4rnl', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(121, 120, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033461, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Checking wild count and state', 'This is a basic command I threw together to see if the wilderness is active or inactive and to see how many players are currently in the wilderness.\n\n[code:1kynu7bg]\n  if(cmd&#46;equalsIgnoreCase(&quot;wild&quot;)) {\n      int wildcount = 0;\n      for(Player p &#58; world&#46;getPlayers()) {\n    if(p&#46;getLocation()&#46;wildernessLevel() &gt; 0) {\n        wildcount++;\n    }\n      }\n      String wildernessState;\n      if(wildcount == 0) {\n    wildernessState = &quot;@red@INACTIVE&quot;;\n      } else {\n    wildernessState = &quot;@gre@ACTIVE&quot;;\n      }\n      if(wildcount == 0) {\n    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The wilderness is currently &quot; + wildernessState + &quot; @whi@with @or1@&quot; + wildcount + &quot; @whi@players!&quot;);\n    return;\n      }\n      if(wildcount == 1) {\n    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The wilderness is currently &quot; + wildernessState + &quot; @whi@with @or1@&quot; + wildcount + &quot; @whi@player!&quot;);\n    return;\n      } else {\n    player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;The wilderness is currently &quot; + wildernessState + &quot; @whi@with @or1@&quot; + wildcount + &quot; @whi@players!&quot;);\n    return;\n      }\n  }\n[/code:1kynu7bg]The command is used like:\n\n[quote:1kynu7bg]\n::wild\n[/quote:1kynu7bg]\n\n[img:1kynu7bg]http&#58;//i41&#46;tinypic&#46;com/tjpc&#46;png[/img:1kynu7bg]\n[img:1kynu7bg]http&#58;//i40&#46;tinypic&#46;com/2ed1h1k&#46;png[/img:1kynu7bg]\n[img:1kynu7bg]http&#58;//i41&#46;tinypic&#46;com/30wv6ki&#46;png[/img:1kynu7bg]', '214db1099e7cc7d50117e7c822db5fe2', 0, 'iIA=', '1kynu7bg', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(122, 121, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033509, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Yong Min''s hide loot command', 'This is client side on Noobscape4, this code is server side.\n\n[code:irkazld5]    if(cmd&#46;equals(&quot;hideloot&quot;)) {\n        if(player&#46;getItemVisibility()) {\n            player&#46;setItemVisibility(false);\n            for(Item i &#58; player&#46;getWatchedItems()&#46;getKnownEntities()) {\n                player&#46;getWatchedItems()&#46;remove(i);\n            }\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Loot visibility is now&#58; @red@Disabled&quot;);\n        } else {\n            player&#46;setItemVisibility(true);\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Loot visibility is now&#58; @gre@Enabled&quot;);\n        }\n    }[/code:irkazld5]The command client-side looks like this:\n[img:irkazld5]http&#58;//i44&#46;tinypic&#46;com/21vkon&#46;png[/img:irkazld5]\n[img:irkazld5]http&#58;//i44&#46;tinypic&#46;com/izs1fo&#46;png[/img:irkazld5]\n\n\nI will be removing the hide loot command in V4, and just keeping the option in the client. If you want to use this command until V4 comes out, then you will also need in your Player class:\n\n[code:irkazld5]\n    /**\n  * Hidden Ground Items\n  */\n    private boolean hiddenItems = true;\n\n    public boolean getHiddenItem() {\n  return hiddenItems;\n    }\n\n    public void setHiddenItem(boolean hiddenitem) {\n  hiddenItems = hiddenitem;\n    }\n[/code:irkazld5]And then change your updateViewedItem method with:\n\n[code:irkazld5]\n    public void updateViewedItems() {\n  List&lt;Item&gt; itemsInView = viewArea&#46;getItemsInView();\n  for (Item i &#58; itemsInView) {\n      if ((!(watchedItems&#46;contains(i))) &amp;&amp; (!(i&#46;isRemoved())) &amp;&amp; (withinRange(i)) &amp;&amp; (i&#46;visibleTo(this)) &amp;&amp; (hiddenItems == true)) {\n    watchedItems&#46;add(i);\n      }\n  }\n    }\n[/code:irkazld5]', '39a3dbb2154cfb12b3ab236b48aa8d32', 0, 'CIA=', 'irkazld5', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(123, 122, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033547, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Yong Min''s admin damage players', '[code:dmq07f9d]    if(cmd&#46;equals(&quot;damage&quot;)) {\n        long PlayerHash = DataConversions&#46;usernameToHash(args&#91;0&#93;);\n        Player p = world&#46;getPlayer(PlayerHash);\n        Player affectedPlayer = world&#46;getPlayer(DataConversions&#46;usernameToHash(args&#91;0&#93;));\n        int damage = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;1&#93;);\n        int newHp = affectedPlayer&#46;getHits() - damage;\n        Random generator = new Random();\n        Scanner in = new Scanner(System&#46;in);\n        int num = generator&#46;nextInt(2) + 1;\n        if(affectedPlayer == null) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid player or maybe they aren''t online?&quot;);\n            return;\n        }\n        if(damage &gt;= 99) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You can only give 98 damage or less to another player&#46;&quot;);\n            return;\n        }\n        if(damage &gt;= affectedPlayer&#46;getCurStat(3)) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid damage or player would die if damaged by that amount&#46;&quot;);\n            return;\n        }\n        if(num == 1 &amp;&amp; damage &gt;= 1) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You have just damaged &quot; + affectedPlayer&#46;getUsername());\n            Projectile projectil = new Projectile(player, affectedPlayer, 1);\n            godSpellObject(affectedPlayer, 33);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setLastDamage(damage);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setHits(newHp);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendStats();\n              ArrayList\n playersToInform = new ArrayList\n();\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(affectedPlayer&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(player&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              for(Player play &#58; playersToInform) {\n                  play&#46;informOfModifiedHits(affectedPlayer);\n            }\n        }    \n        if(num == 2 &amp;&amp; damage &gt;= 1) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You have just damaged &quot; + affectedPlayer&#46;getUsername());\n            Projectile projectil = new Projectile(player, affectedPlayer, 1);\n            godSpellObject(affectedPlayer, 34);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setLastDamage(damage);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setHits(newHp);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendStats();\n              ArrayList\n playersToInform = new ArrayList\n();\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(affectedPlayer&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(player&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              for(Player play &#58; playersToInform) {\n                  play&#46;informOfModifiedHits(affectedPlayer);\n            }\n        }\n        if(num == 3 &amp;&amp; damage &gt;= 1) {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;You have just damaged &quot; + affectedPlayer&#46;getUsername());\n            Projectile projectil = new Projectile(player, affectedPlayer, 1);\n            godSpellObject(affectedPlayer, 35);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setLastDamage(damage);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;setHits(newHp);\n            affectedPlayer&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendStats();\n              ArrayList\n playersToInform = new ArrayList\n();\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(affectedPlayer&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              playersToInform&#46;addAll(player&#46;getViewArea()&#46;getPlayersInView());\n              for(Player play &#58; playersToInform) {\n                  play&#46;informOfModifiedHits(affectedPlayer);\n            }\n        }\n    }[/code:dmq07f9d]\n\n\nYou will want these too:\n\n[code:dmq07f9d]\n    public void godSpellObject(Mob affectedPlayer, int spell) {\n        switch(spell) {\n            case 33&#58;\n                GameObject guthix = new GameObject(affectedPlayer&#46;getLocation(), 1142, 0, 0);\n                world&#46;registerGameObject(guthix);\n                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ObjectRemover(guthix, 500));\n                break;\n            case 34&#58;\n                GameObject sara = new GameObject(affectedPlayer&#46;getLocation(), 1031, 0, 0);\n                world&#46;registerGameObject(sara);\n                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ObjectRemover(sara, 500));\n                break;\n            case 35&#58;\n                GameObject zammy = new GameObject(affectedPlayer&#46;getLocation(), 1036, 0, 0);\n                world&#46;registerGameObject(zammy);\n                world&#46;getDelayedEventHandler()&#46;add(new ObjectRemover(zammy, 500));\n                break;    \n            }\n    }\n[/code:dmq07f9d][code:dmq07f9d]\nimport org&#46;rscdaemon&#46;server&#46;event&#46;ObjectRemover;\n[/code:dmq07f9d]', '6e27afc5c387580774f8e1c2e4fbdfbd', 0, 'AIA=', 'dmq07f9d', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(124, 123, 12, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306033561, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Yong Min''s teleport towns command', 'This will come with Noobscape4 but for now at least:\n\n[code:2qcopeav]    if((cmd&#46;equals(&quot;teleport&quot;)) &amp;&amp; (player&#46;isPMod())) {\n        if(args&#46;length != 2) {\n            if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;modroom&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(72, 1641, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;edgeville&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(225, 447, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;varrock&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(122, 503, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;falador&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(313, 550, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;seers&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(501, 455, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;catherby&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(440, 500, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;yanille&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(587, 761, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;karamja&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(371, 695, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;ardougne&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(585, 621, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;draynor&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(214, 632, false);\n            } else if(args&#91;0&#93;&#46;equals(&quot;lumbridge&quot;)) {\n                player&#46;teleport(122, 647, false);\n            } else {\n                player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid location&quot;);\n            }\n        } else if((args&#46;length == 2) &amp;&amp; (player&#46;isMod())) {\n            int x = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;0&#93;);\n            int y = Integer&#46;parseInt(args&#91;1&#93;);\n        if(world&#46;withinWorld(x, y)) {\n            Logger&#46;mod(player&#46;getUsername() + &quot; teleported from &quot; + player&#46;getLocation()&#46;toString() + &quot; to (&quot; + x + &quot;, &quot; + y + &quot;)&quot;);\n            player&#46;teleport(x, y, true);\n        }\n        else {\n            player&#46;getActionSender()&#46;sendMessage(&quot;Invalid coordinates!&quot;);\n        }\n        return;\n        }\n    }[/code:2qcopeav]', '0d7d43d3874825d39e6b9d03c506906f', 0, 'AIA=', '2qcopeav', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(127, 124, 8, 2, 0, '65.190.15.53', 1306075555, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Sprite Editing', '[img:1pn9y01s]http&#58;//i&#46;imgur&#46;com/85auV&#46;png[/img:1pn9y01s]\n\nCopy your sprites.wk file to the Sprite Editor folder.\n\nUnpack your sprites.wk file with run_unpacker.bat\n\nCopy 1339.spr from Sprite Editor/unpack/dat/ to RSCD Sprite Editor/unpack/\n\nEdit Sprite Editor/src/spriteeditor/SpritePacker.java\n\nReplace:\n[code:1pn9y01s]public static String NEW_DIR = &quot;&#46;/sprites/&quot;;[/code:1pn9y01s]\n\nWith:\n[code:1pn9y01s]public static String NEW_DIR = &quot;&#46;/unpack/&quot;;[/code:1pn9y01s]\n\n(This is my personal preference for the unpack folder)\n\nRun Compile.bat\n\nRun the run_editor.bat and click the Load Sprite button. Select 1339.spr from the Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder.\n\nLook at the bottom bar and make a notepad text file containing the values it gives.\n\nPackage, ID, Shift, X-Shift, Y-Shift, Width-2, and Height-2 are all that you need to write down.\n\nClick the Save Image button and save the new sprite image to the Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder.\n\n**Make sure you append .PNG to the end of the file name.**\n\nQuit the sprite editor and open up your image editing program. I use Paint.Net as its free and just as good as Photoshop in most areas.\n\nEdit the sprite PNG file from the Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder as you wish and save it.\n\nOpen run_editor.bat and click the Load Image button. Navigate to the Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder.\n\nNormally you should be able to edit the bottom bar fields with the information you saved on your notepad text file from before but for whatever reason, it does not save it to your .spr sprite file.\n\nClick the Save Sprite button and navigate to your Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder. Save your sprite as 1339.spr and always make sure you append .spr to the end of the new sprite file name. If you don''t, the sprite packer will not see it.\n\nNavigate to Sprite Editor/unpack/ and open 1339.spr with 7zip. It is a tar.gz archive, just like the .wk files from your client cache are.\n\nExtract the 1339 file (no file type) to your desktop and open it with notepad++ or wordpad. (Not regular notepad as that doesn''t show the lines correctly and bunches it up into unreadable text)\n\nYou will notice this is an XML file. Scroll to the very bottom to where it reads:\n[code:1pn9y01s]&lt;width&gt;321&lt;/width&gt;\n  &lt;height&gt;163&lt;/height&gt;\n  &lt;packageName&gt;unknown&lt;/packageName&gt;\n  &lt;id&gt;-1&lt;/id&gt;\n  &lt;requiresShift&gt;false&lt;/requiresShift&gt;\n  &lt;xShift&gt;0&lt;/xShift&gt;\n  &lt;yShift&gt;0&lt;/yShift&gt;\n  &lt;width2&gt;0&lt;/width2&gt;\n  &lt;height2&gt;0&lt;/height2&gt;\n&lt;/spriteeditor&#46;Sprite&gt;[/code:1pn9y01s]\n\nYou want to ignore the first width and height lines. Where it reads packageName, delete the word &quot;unknown&quot; if your sprite editor had a blank in that box before. For the rest, fill it out exactly as you wrote down on your notepad text file. When finished, save the XML file and drag it back into the 7zip file manager to update the compressed XML file inside the 1339.spr archive.\n\nNavigate to Sprite Editor/ and open the run_packer.bat file. Select your Sprites.wk file and click Open.\n\nIt should only pack the 1339.spr as that is what is sitting in the Sprite Editor/unpack/ folder. Beware of images that are too large, such as a background for a client. If it is too large, it will crash the sprite packer.\n\nNote: if you paint a sprite with the same shade of black that is in the background of the sprite, whatever you paint black will become transparent.\n\nThe overlay function in the sprite editor is neat to play with but does not save any colors to the sprite.', '5144fb9c457f8c5bf93810e17549e668', 0, 'CIA=', '1pn9y01s', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
